000 kr., som er angivet i skemaet, men under de ca. 900.000 kr., som fremgår af næste indkomstbeløb.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"680\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"76px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"87px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"87px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"87px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"87px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"87px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:15px;\">\r\n                     <td colspan=\"6\" style=\"border-left: none;border-right: none;border-top: none;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"680\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:15px;\">\r\n                     <td colspan=\"6\" style=\"border-left: none;border-right: none;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;text-align: left\" valign=\"top\" width=\"680\">\r\n                        <div class=\"Overskriftstekst1\">Uddannelsesbidrag: Vejledende indkomstbeløb for 2013</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:15px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"101\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;b